distro


Controls suffixing of Otter release directory name during build.
Override by passing $otter_suffix in environment.

 arch   : suffix with "-$( uname -m )"
 distro : suffix with "-$( lsb_release -sc )"

Matches are detected with Bash =~ operator, without word boundaries,
and applied in the order specified in the build system.

See otter_ipath_get in _otterlace.sh shared functions.
